        <section id="deps-spr">
            <h>specifier</h>
            <p>Like other common nouns, <g>taigh</g> can occur with a <a
                    href="?xx=nouns/determiners">determiner</a> as pre-specifier.</p>
            <p>Examples with the <a href="?xx=nouns/definite_article">definite article</a> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha Seònaid anns <m>an taigh</m>.</gd>
                        <tr>Janet is in the house.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                    </li>
                <li>
                    <gd>Càit a bheil <m>an taigh</m> mór? Tha <m>an taigh</m> mór air a’ chnoc
                        àrd.</gd>
                    <tr>Where is the big house? The big house is on the tall hill.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 21 [229]</ref>
                </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section id="deps-mods">
            <h>modifiers</h>
            <p>Like other nouns, <g>taigh</g> can occur with an (attributive) <a
                    href="?xx=adjectives/adjectives">adjective</a> (post-)modifier.</p>
            <p>Some examples – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Dé tha air a’ chnoc? Tha <m>taigh mór</m> air a’ chnoc.</gd>
                        <tr>What is on the hill? There is a big house on the hill.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h>uses</h>
        <section id="uses-sbj">
            <h>subject</h>
            <p>Like other nouns, <g>taigh</g> can be used as the subject of a <a
                    href="?xx=verbs/verbs">verb</a>.</p>
            <p>Examples with <a href="?gd=bi"><g>bi</g></a> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Dé tha air a’ chnoc? Tha <m>taigh</m> mór air a’ chnoc.</gd>
                        <tr>What is on the hill? There is a big house on the hill.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
                    </li>
                <li>
                    <gd>Càit a bheil an <m>taigh</m> mór? Tha an <m>taigh</m> mór air a’ chnoc
                        àrd.</gd>
                    <tr>Where is the big house? The big house is on the tall hill.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 21 [229]</ref>
                </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </section>
